<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Tue, 19 Apr 2022 10:18:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>Switch 版 Game Boy 模擬器截圖曝光，將支援 Switch Online</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/19/game-boy-switch-online/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=game-boy-switch-online</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 19 Apr 2022 10:18:00 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Game Boy]]></category><category><![CDATA[Switch]]></category><category><![CDATA[任天堂]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1096292</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>有傳任天堂計劃將 Game Boy 遊戲加入 Nintendo Switch Online 中，開放予已訂閱的 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>有傳任天堂計劃將 Game Boy 遊戲加入 Nintendo Switch Online 中，開放予已訂閱的玩家。而網上亦有流傳遊戲的截圖，令可信性大增，惟任天堂未有回應有關傳言。</p><p>據 Neowin 報道，Twitter 用戶 Trash_Bandatcoot （@trashbandatcoot）指從洩露文件中可見，主要負責開發任天堂官方模擬器的歐洲研發團隊 NERD，正開發代號為「Sloop」的 Game Boy Advance 模擬器及「Hiyoko」的 Game Boy 模擬器，稱任天堂正開發於 Switch Online 的 Game Boy、Game Boy Color 及 Game Boy Advance 的模擬器。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">&#8230;called Sloop, and the 7z archive is called Hiyoko, which is a Game Boy emulator, with all Game Boy games being separate applications. These emulators are developed by NERD (Nintendo Europe Research &amp; Development), and are both functional, albeit with a few bugs. (2/?) <a href="https://t.co/RRUAVvz2BX">pic.twitter.com/RRUAVvz2BX</a></p><p>&mdash; Trash_Bandatcoot (@trashbandatcoot) <a href="https://twitter.com/trashbandatcoot/status/1516116505842302981?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 18, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>Trash_Bandatcoot 更分享了 Switch 上的 Game Boy 遊戲截圖，圖片上的模擬器已幾乎完成，令傳言的可信性大增。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">And here&#39;s some screenshots of it actually working if anyone is curious lol. <a href="https://t.co/RcAULaFX07">pic.twitter.com/RcAULaFX07</a></p><p>&mdash; Trash_Bandatcoot (@trashbandatcoot) <a href="https://twitter.com/trashbandatcoot/status/1516111526075289601?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 18, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>此外，Trash_Bandatcoot 更稱 Switch 上的 Game Boy 遊戲皆為單獨的應用程序，並附上於 Switch 主機開啟 Game Boy Advance 模擬器的影片，但發布後隨即被刪除。</p><p>不過任天堂未有回應有關在 Switch Online 上開放 Game Boy 和 Game Boy Advanced 模擬器的傳聞。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.neowin.net/news/nintendo039s-game-boy-and-gba-emulators-039sloop039-and-039hiyoko039-for-switch-online-have-leaked/">Neowin</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
